      • performQuery

        protected com.google.common.util.concurrent.ListenableFuture<List<MatcherGroup>> performQuery(String sectionName,
                                                                                  boolean createIfEmpty)
        Performs this query, traversing inheritance if necessary. Duplicate groups may be present in the result if the same group is relevant in multiple places in the inheritance hierarchy.
        Parameters:
        sectionName - The name of the section being looked up in this query.
        createIfEmpty - Create a new matcher group if none match
        Returns:
        the relevant matcher groups
